# 📖 Project Overview

The GSM/GPS-Based Vehicle Location Tracking System with Accident Detection is an embedded system designed for real-time vehicle monitoring, theft prevention, and emergency response.

The system combines GPS technology, GSM communication, and Arduino-based control to provide:

- Real-time vehicle location
- Accident detection
- SMS alerts
- Remote engine immobilization
- Google Maps tracking
- Door monitoring
- Ignition monitoring
- Vehicle security

---

# 🎯 Objectives

- Track vehicle location in real time.
- Detect accidents automatically.
- Send emergency SMS alerts.
- Prevent vehicle theft.
- Allow remote vehicle immobilization.
- Monitor vehicle status.

